{"id": "ChIJNx4Y_LiAhYARFI7FDc60IAc", "rating": 4.7, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 2125, "displayName": {"text": "Udon Mugizo - SF", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Simply decorated Japanese noodle specialist serves up a menu of udon, tempura & mochi.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJNx4Y_LiAhYARFI7FDc60IAc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xJNU9UbHhXR2hEUkVoR09EZG9Wa0YxUTJwNVUzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This restaurant is tucked into a mall in Japantown and really delivers on flavor! The udon was fresh and delicious and the onigiri appetizer was one of my favorite things anywhere. I got the nabeyaki udon and really enjoyed the mushroom in it too. The portions were generous and service was so friendly. The wait time can get long (we waited 30 minutes) but we put our names on the waitlist and explored the mall in the meantime. I would go back!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This restaurant is tucked into a mall in Japantown and really delivers on flavor! The udon was fresh and delicious and the onigiri appetizer was one of my favorite things anywhere. I got the nabeyaki udon and really enjoyed the mushroom in it too. The portions were generous and service was so friendly. The wait time can get long (we waited 30 minutes) but we put our names on the waitlist and explored the mall in the meantime. I would go back!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kiran Suresh", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110317173707520048533/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3AkvW9JOqGEwekcuyC4m9PKFVF-zVa7N5VdObmi0UPHI_0nsBtA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-26T20:38:23.115649971Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xJNU9UbHhXR2hEUkVoR09EZG9Wa0YxUTJwNVUzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xJNU9UbHhXR2hEUkVoR09EZG9Wa0YxUTJwNVUzYxAB!2m1!1s0x808580b8fc181e37:0x720b4ce0dc58e14"}, {"name": "places/ChIJNx4Y_LiAhYARFI7FDc60IAc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xSWE9IRlRWSHB5VFhOd1FuTmpaMUpTWm1kUlNIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Peak lunch was about a 30min wait so we were shopping diff stores in the mall. The food came out quick. I def recommend the mentaiko creamy udon which is light and has seafood taste and the curry udon for a beefy rich taste. The noodles were a yummy texture. The tempura was good, but i prefer more of a light airy batter. Jeff was our waiter and was excellent, super nice!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Peak lunch was about a 30min wait so we were shopping diff stores in the mall. The food came out quick. I def recommend the mentaiko creamy udon which is light and has seafood taste and the curry udon for a beefy rich taste. The noodles were a yummy texture. The tempura was good, but i prefer more of a light airy batter. Jeff was our waiter and was excellent, super nice!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ashley Jung", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117632132272749635251/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsBQaLHM-r7NuacOrJJQKIMl1LlQDSFmfoKPCD2Q-HtReokZD4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-31T01:35:22.453625094Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xSWE9IRlRWSHB5VFhOd1FuTmpaMUpTWm1kUlNIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xSWE9IRlRWSHB5VFhOd1FuTmpaMUpTWm1kUlNIYxAB!2m1!1s0x808580b8fc181e37:0x720b4ce0dc58e14"}, {"name": "places/ChIJNx4Y_LiAhYARFI7FDc60IAc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wR1ZXYzFVVEpEUWt3dE9YSklPRWhyV20xaldGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "It is better to get your name on their list! With our name on the list, a party of 5, we had to wait 40 min! It was middle of holidays, the mall was full.\nWe had three different udons and all of them were really tasty! All ingredients were fresh, the noodle was cooked perfectly and the broth was amazing delicious! Our appetizer was the takoyaki, we forgot to take pics, we ate them too fast, so good they were!\nThe service was very good, all attendants were polite and they made sure to accommodate well.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It is better to get your name on their list! With our name on the list, a party of 5, we had to wait 40 min! It was middle of holidays, the mall was full.\nWe had three different udons and all of them were really tasty! All ingredients were fresh, the noodle was cooked perfectly and the broth was amazing delicious! Our appetizer was the takoyaki, we forgot to take pics, we ate them too fast, so good they were!\nThe service was very good, all attendants were polite and they made sure to accommodate well.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Karin Yamaki", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104934505808296742138/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXmIlP4TH0lKpiyDBNRTMEOeA8h5keruKeHrulb4a7WrcwBD5Mpg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-02T16:35:21.872681041Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wR1ZXYzFVVEpEUWt3dE9YSklPRWhyV20xaldGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wR1ZXYzFVVEpEUWt3dE9YSklPRWhyV20xaldGRRAB!2m1!1s0x808580b8fc181e37:0x720b4ce0dc58e14"}, {"name": "places/ChIJNx4Y_LiAhYARFI7FDc60IAc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GWmVuVnphMWd4Ykd0UFJYUXRUa0pEYkhwdWNXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Went here on a whim and was very satisfied.\n\nFood: I got the salmon spinach cream sauce udon and the broth was soo good. I don't like cheese and not a fan of green onion eitger, this bowl came with a lot of both and I wish I had scooped it out but I figured I'd eat it as it's supposed to and I ended up pushing them to the side as I ate. It wasn't bad, I just don't prefer them. Noodles were chewy (in the best way) and the salmon was also well seasoned. I nearly drank up the broth by itself.\nI also ordered the lychee soda that came in a pouch with some kinda light up device inside. I didn't care too much for the presentation, but the drink itself was good. Not too sweet and good flavor.\n\nService: service was quick, I got seated right away. The host asked if I needed recommendations, but I already knew what I wanted.\n\nAtmosphere: the layout was good, nice flow from entrance to seating and kitchen. Everything looked clean and well kept. Noise level was moderate, you can talk in a normal voice and be able to hear each other if you're with a group.\n\nI'd come back again to try the mentai cream. Or stick with the spinach because it really was delicious", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Went here on a whim and was very satisfied.\n\nFood: I got the salmon spinach cream sauce udon and the broth was soo good. I don't like cheese and not a fan of green onion eitger, this bowl came with a lot of both and I wish I had scooped it out but I figured I'd eat it as it's supposed to and I ended up pushing them to the side as I ate. It wasn't bad, I just don't prefer them. Noodles were chewy (in the best way) and the salmon was also well seasoned. I nearly drank up the broth by itself.\nI also ordered the lychee soda that came in a pouch with some kinda light up device inside. I didn't care too much for the presentation, but the drink itself was good. Not too sweet and good flavor.\n\nService: service was quick, I got seated right away. The host asked if I needed recommendations, but I already knew what I wanted.\n\nAtmosphere: the layout was good, nice flow from entrance to seating and kitchen. Everything looked clean and well kept. Noise level was moderate, you can talk in a normal voice and be able to hear each other if you're with a group.\n\nI'd come back again to try the mentai cream. Or stick with the spinach because it really was delicious", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "LN", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114633571851024564716/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLf7QS5zSbB2UGzGMQMDDmCoAhg4HwRQYiQ0e-80Pn-vPh3A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-05T00:12:21.794029860Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GWmVuVnphMWd4Ykd0UFJYUXRUa0pEYkhwdWNXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GWmVuVnphMWd4Ykd0UFJYUXRUa0pEYkhwdWNXYxAB!2m1!1s0x808580b8fc181e37:0x720b4ce0dc58e14"}, {"name": "places/ChIJNx4Y_LiAhYARFI7FDc60IAc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSclpIbHhiRTFyWVMxaFkxbGhlSFpFVFd0dldGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "One of our go to spots for udon. Their signature mentai cream udon is my favorite. Thick saucy cream sauce on the udon is the best. A bit on the heavy side but then it was very tasty. I also like their katsu donburi. Comes with a mini udon so it will definitely be very filling. Our server was super nice and tentative as well. His name is Jeff. Iykyk 😆\n\nCame back a week later (doctors appointment at Kaiser). Had the curry udon and it was decent. Portions were big and Janny was such a nice and attentive server as well!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "One of our go to spots for udon. Their signature mentai cream udon is my favorite. Thick saucy cream sauce on the udon is the best. A bit on the heavy side but then it was very tasty. I also like their katsu donburi. Comes with a mini udon so it will definitely be very filling. Our server was super nice and tentative as well. His name is Jeff. Iykyk 😆\n\nCame back a week later (doctors appointment at Kaiser). Had the curry udon and it was decent. Portions were big and Janny was such a nice and attentive server as well!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Pak Ko", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103471622463750626169/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjm2HlG3-UALZQAwXGSdhg_0E7BtHtnBIIDOt-jf0UyDZNvomE-A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-12T19:10:57.848750248Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSclpIbHhiRTFyWVMxaFkxbGhlSFpFVFd0dldGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSclpIbHhiRTFyWVMxaFkxbGhlSFpFVFd0dldGRRAB!2m1!1s0x808580b8fc181e37:0x720b4ce0dc58e14"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJNx4Y_LiAhYARFI7FDc60IAc/photos/AWCwydgcyS5-h6d_HLafffC9LYHwBMlcbw97YMpUls2rL3EU3ikF3cggSmTRt2SMzwJmJXVYur-sRkK0jUgl-RpUooEcVkCTuuqXgexolP0iCyoF9CQtj8AwkmwBYDM3oeJut0AsS0fuLJZM-Xkmr3GnjilqfinnFw1n_tF1HwHe0QC4YOedcyywl04OSLkLyMycXvhtq9HRYw_tQLFcoKw0gTj8NpIbE5uiqMFD4ApxIv0mNeWGChzvarV8JaY73SohWkJpKTngx71lbISqfFIEQn_OnwBHlRq2HhjTqGclpXcck4ItK7BmufxEdABxXr8X7xRT03Wz7M1imKpdkZK2SdZo5G43_TnWPI_M153eVKN9s7MmLETn_9sOlwtcnqYCPPw455iO_SRQsQimN6CD1IZXnVFKJDDQZmjSZXLn3pLTN-_PtByYn3hOy0gHeriL", "widthPx": 4800, "heightPx": 3200, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Udon Mugizo - SF", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/101549114008159160327", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVemqnBRXeCygZUppI2j9C-v_rnfZ7QMl7XRud5N0rdhm0he4=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/